. Additional bonus damage<br>will be dealt relative to the damage taken while<br>Crimson Garden is active. If the user\'s HP is above<br>60% of max HP when using this skill, they will take<br>damage equal to 20% of their maximum HP.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 820 \\u00d7 2 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 4,730<br>Counterattack Damage: 1,100% of damage taken<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/af68964937fa01084c3d0747e6c77dda2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Dragon Haste +15%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases dragon gauge fill rate by 15%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/368330649dd4e9c07abc8582ae510ece2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Flame) HP Below 60% = HP Regen VI<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Flame: <br>grants them an HP regen buff for 20 seconds<br>when their HP drops to 60%. After activating,<br>this ability will not activate again for 30 seconds.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/fd589517c61c65312e1509e13a36cd412.png\\"><\/span><span>Crimson Oath<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases damage to scorchrent enemies<br>by 15% and force strike damage by 50%.<br><br>Using Road to Glory grants the user the<br>\\"Crimson Glory\\" effect and a strength amp<br>with a maximum team amp level of two.<br>After this amp is granted, this ability<br>will not grant it again for 30 seconds.<br><br>When Crimson Glory is active, the user\'s<br>next force strike will deal additional damage<br>and inflict scorchrend.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/9f9540aa3b892c485f82bfd1ef78b1b72.png\\"><\/span><span>Potent Stun Res +100%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to stun by 100%.<br>When the user is hit by an attack that would have<br>stunned them, their strength is increased by 15%<br>for 10 seconds. After activating, this buff will not<br>activate again for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/b2f1d14494e80343f38734ca9a2b72842.png\\"><\/span><span>Striking Haste +15%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases skill gauge fill rate by 15%<br>when the user\'s force strikes connect.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.<\/div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1629093600,"prev_article_id":"2357","next_article_id":"2408","image_path":"","update_time":1628743763}}}'